## Final Database Migration Principle

> Migrations are immutable, sequential, and reversible. Treat production data with extreme care.

If a migration risks data loss or production downtime without clear mitigation, it must be rejected.

> **Domain READMEs document schema evolution.** Every migration should be documented in the domain's README with rationale and rollback strategy.
